<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee2c9b39-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s387a"><num value="387a">§ 387a.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated each fiscal year necessary appropriations to enable the Secretary of Agriculture to carry on the experiments contemplated by <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s387">section 387 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee2c9b3a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1928-03-19/ch228/s3">Mar. 19, 1928, ch. 228, § 3</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/323">45 Stat. 323</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
